Class SocksPropertySpecConstants

java.lang.Object
com.github.jh3nd3rs0n.jargyle.client.SocksPropertySpecConstants
public final class SocksPropertySpecConstants extends Object
SOCKS specific PropertySpec constants.

  • Field Summary

    Fields
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    static final PropertySpec<Oid>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_MECHANISM_OID
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.mechanismOid: the Oid for the object ID for the GSS-API authentication mechanism to the SOCKS server (default value is 1.2.840.113554.1.2.2).
    static final PropertySpec<Boolean>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_NEC_REFERENCE_IMPL
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.necReferenceImpl: the Boolean value to indicate if the exchange of the GSS-API protection level negotiation must be unprotected should the SOCKS server use the NEC reference implementation (default value is false).
    static final PropertySpec<CommaSeparatedValues>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_PROTECTION_LEVELS
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.protectionLevels: the CommaSeparatedValues for acceptable protection levels after GSS-API authentication with the SOCKS server (The first is preferred while the remaining are acceptable if the server does not accept the first) (default value is REQUIRED_INTEG_AND_CONF,REQUIRED_INTEG,NONE).
    static final PropertySpec<String>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_SERVICE_NAME
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.serviceName: the GSS-API service name for the SOCKS server.
    static final PropertySpec<Boolean>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_SUGGESTED_CONF
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.suggestedConf: the Boolean value for the suggested privacy (or confidentiality) state for GSS-API messages sent after GSS-API authentication with the SOCKS server (applicable if the negotiated protection level is SELECTIVE_INTEG_OR_CONF) (default value is true).
    static final PropertySpec<Integer>
    SOCKS_GSSAPIAUTHMETHOD_SUGGESTED_INTEG
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.gssapiauthmethod.suggestedInteg: the Integer for the suggested quality-of-protection (or integrity) value for GSS-API messages sent after GSS-API authentication with the SOCKS server (applicable if the negotiated protection level is SELECTIVE_INTEG_OR_CONF) (default value is 0).
    static final PropertySpec<CommaSeparatedValues>
    SOCKS_METHODS
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.methods: the CommaSeparatedValues for acceptable authentication methods to the SOCKS server (default value is NO_AUTHENTICATION_REQUIRED).
    static final PropertySpec<Boolean>
    SOCKS_SOCKS_DATAGRAM_SOCKET_CLIENT_INFO_UNAVAILABLE
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.socksDatagramSocket.clientInfoUnavailable: the Boolean value to indicate if the client information expected to be used to send UDP datagrams (address and port) is unavailable to be sent to the SOCKS server (an address and port of all zeros is sent instead) (default value is false).
    static final PropertySpec<EncryptedPassword>
    SOCKS_USERPASSAUTHMETHOD_PASSWORD
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.userpassauthmethod.password: the EncryptedPassword for the password to be used to access the SOCKS server.
    static final PropertySpec<String>
    SOCKS_USERPASSAUTHMETHOD_USERNAME
    PropertySpec constant for socksClient.socks.userpassauthmethod.username: the username to be used to access the SOCKS server.
